{
  "stem": "4570.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we went-- we must have gone before-- I, I don't know when Mengele was or when I dropped the bread.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I must have dropped the bread and the pate before Mengele.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know it was a terribly dusty road-- not dusty, muddy road.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were walking on that road.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the women from the barracks were screaming at us, throw us your, your watches and your jewelry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, I wouldn't have thrown anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, what would they have done with it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Actually, they could do-- I think there was a lot of black market going on in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I didn't want to do anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the guard-- one of the guards that was walking alongside shouted at the woman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the woman didn't go into the barrack as he asked her, and so he shot her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was the first time I saw somebody being shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she fell down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In mid September, she had only a little smock on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was naked underneath.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as she fell, the whole smock fell away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there she was naked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I got such a scare, I dropped my bread and my pate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because I thought.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I better not break the rules in this place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I think we came to, to, where, where this table was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And on it was this SS man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were five, five, fives.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But then, before we came to the table, we had to go one by one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I noticed my girlfriend, one of my girlfriends-- it was a very beautiful Dutch girl, Helen Van Leven, she was called.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she also went in the transport as a volunteer, because she had fallen in love with a Czech guy.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
